column2: You are about to delete your ship
de: You are about to delete your ship
es: Estás a punto de borrar tu nave
fr: Vous êtes sur le point de supprimer votre vaisseau
pt: Você está prestes a excluir sua nave

column2: All changes will be lost. Do you wish to continue?
de: All changes will be lost. Do you wish to continue?
es: Todos los cambios se perderán ¿Quieres continuar?
fr: Toutes les modifications seront perdues. Voulez-vous continuer ?
pt: Todas as alterações serão perdidas. Você deseja continuar?
zh: 所有更改都将丢失。你确认要继续吗？

column2: You are about to reset your ship
de: You are about to reset your ship
es: Estás a punto de restablecer tu nave
fr: Vous êtes sur le point de réinitialiser votre vaisseau
pt: Você está prestes a redefinir sua nave

fr: Copier le vaisseau dans le presse-papiers
pt: Copiar nave para a área de transferência

de: Fügen Sie alle zur Wunschliste hinzu
es: Agregar todo a la lista de deseos
fr: Tout ajouter à la liste de souhaits
pt: Adicionar tudo à lista de desejos

es: Agregar los cambios a la lista de deseos
fr: Ajouter changements à la liste de souhaits
pt: Adicionar alterado à lista de desejos

column2: You can drag modules into different slots. If you hold CTRL while dragging, the module will be copied instead of moved.
de: You can drag modules into different slots. If you hold CTRL while dragging, the module will be copied instead of moved.
es: Puedes arrastrar módulos en diferentes ranuras. Si mantienes la tecla CTRL al arrastrar, el módulo sera copiado en vez de movido
fr: You can drag modules into different slots. If you hold CTRL while dragging, the module will be copied instead of moved.
pt: Você pode arrastar módulos para diferentes slots. Se você segurar CTRL enquanto arrasta, o módulo será copiado em vez de movido.
ru: Вы можете перетаскивать модули в разные слоты. Зажав CTRL во время перетягивания, вы скопируете модуль.
zh: 你可以将模块拖动至不同的槽位。如果在拖动时按住CTRL，那么模块将被复制而非移动。

column2: By pressing ALT you can freeze the UI, so you can move your mouse freely around.
de: By pressing ALT you can freeze the UI, so you can move your mouse freely around.
es: Pulsando ALT puedes congelar la interfaz pudiendo mover el ratón libremente.
fr: En appuyant sur ALT, vous pouvez geler l’interface utilisateur afin de déplacer votre souris librement.
pt: Ao pressionar ALT, você pode congelar a IU, o que permite mover o mouse livremente.
ru: Зажав ALT вы можете заморозить интерфейс и свободно двигать мышкой.
zh: 按住ALT可以冻结界面，这样你就可以随意移动鼠标了。

column2: Legacy modules can be stored for later reuse with the button that will be visible above the module specs. Legacy modules can be managed under Settings.
de: Legacy modules can be stored for later reuse with the button that will be visible above the module specs. Legacy modules can be managed under Settings.
es: Los módulos legacy pueden ser almacenados para ser reutilizados posteriormente con el botón que estará visible sobre las especificaciones del módulo. Los módulos Legacy pueden ser administraos en Ajustes.
fr: Legacy modules can be stored for later reuse with the button that will be visible above the module specs. Legacy modules can be managed under Settings.
pt: Módulos legados podem ser armazenados para reutilização posterior com o botão que ficará visível acima das especificações do módulo. Módulos legados podem ser gerenciados em Configurações.
ru: Модули Legacy можно сохранить для последующего повторного использования с помощью кнопки, которая будет видна над спецификациями модуля. Модулями Legacy можно управлять в Настройках.
zh: Legacy 模块可以被存储起来并在以后通过模块选项上方可见的按钮重新使用。Legacy 模块可在“设置”下管理。

column2: Live mode will autoconfigure the settings to match the current state in-game. This only works for the current ship.
de: Live mode will autoconfigure the settings to match the current state in-game. This only works for the current ship.
es: El Modo LIVE se autoconfigurará en ajustes para coincidir con el estado actual del juego. Esto solo funciona para la nave actual.
fr: Live mode will autoconfigure the settings to match the current state in-game. This only works for the current ship.
pt: O modo ao vivo irá autoconfigurar as configurações para corresponder ao estado atual no jogo. Isso só funciona para a nave atual.
ru: Live mode автоматически установит настройки, чтобы повторить нынешнее состояние в игре. Это работает только для активного корабля.
zh: 实时模式将自动配置设置以匹配当前游戏状态。这只适用于当前船只。

column2: Module changes are tracked. If a module state is saved, it will be colored in white and yellow. Any changes to the module, blueprint or experimental effect will turn the color to blue. These changes are considered when creating a wishlist.
de: Module changes are tracked. If a module state is saved, it will be colored in white and yellow. Any changes to the module, blueprint or experimental effect will turn the color to blue. These changes are considered when creating a wishlist.
es: Module changes are tracked. If a module state is saved, it will be colored in white and yellow. Any changes to the module, blueprint or experimental effect will turn the color to blue. These changes are considered when creating a wishlist.
fr: Module changes are tracked. If a module state is saved, it will be colored in white and yellow. Any changes to the module, blueprint or experimental effect will turn the color to blue. These changes are considered when creating a wishlist.
pt: Module changes are tracked. If a module state is saved, it will be colored in white and yellow. Any changes to the module, blueprint or experimental effect will turn the color to blue. These changes are considered when creating a wishlist.
ru: Изменения модулей отслеживаются. Если состояние модуля сохранено, то оно будет окрашено в белый и желтый. Любые изменения в модуле, чертеже или экспериментальном эффекте превратят цвет в синий. Эти изменения учитываются при создании списка желаний.
zh: 模块变化将被记录。如果一个模块的状态被保存，那么它将被显示为白色或黄色。对该模块的任何改变，包括改造蓝图和实验效果都会将颜色变为蓝色。这些变化将在创建愿望单时被运用。

es: Exclusivo de la tienda de ARX
Módulo de Logro de la Comunidad
